{"tid":1636537,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【和理非新戰線！】同我入黎睇哂佢！！","createTime":"2019-10-07T18:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T13:38:39.000Z","uid":177088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"289a08d51770a5f48f8ab93c471e6a8e889a178c","tid":1636537,"uid":177088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:25:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ob3wLuLrIU0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fob3wLuLrIU0&d=wXQbzQ6sjjdDHWUhljjVf8%2BSO5qySt9BI5W58Aqq%2Fug%3D&h=0f8ab2ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ob3wLuLrIU0</a><br />\n<br />\n佢講緊既係中共對台灣既資訊戰（即統戰工作），但做法根本同對香港一模一樣。<br />\n<br />\n第一，透過國安部既黑客攻擊獲取台灣重要個人私隱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VXye4Fn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVXye4Fn.png&h=35f2b3a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二，透過統戰部<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Butnt7O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FButnt7O.png&h=4f8e1f00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一方面呢，會經營大量既content farm <br />\n另一方面又呢到提到啲平價旅遊團，加你入群組繼而發放大量假新聞洗你腦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VscfO9Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVscfO9Y.png&h=b0330c6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第三，有個叫解放軍戰略支援部。佢地就係係facebook youtube 新聞下面成日見到個班五毛啦，同時都係依家影響緊連登風向既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦了解完佢地既行動模式，咁又可以點呢！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>我地要開一條和理非既新戰線！對抗中共統戰，唔可以由任由佢地單方面滲入香港，我地要反攻大陸！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pkGwnw0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpkGwnw0.png&h=66b5bad3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WfyuTDG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWfyuTDG.png&h=e2bc2201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n方向：<br />\n<br />\n1. 組成一個戰略中心，建議telegram<br />\n<br />\n2.揾出中共手下既內容農場/youtube channel/facebook page, 組織dislike, block and report 行動。<br />\n<br />\n3. 招打手，攻擊五毛，係大陸人聚集既網上瘋狂留言。<br />\n<br />\n4. <strong>製造針對內地既文宣，我地已經有國際戰線，點解仲未有大陸戰線？唔反攻大陸點支爆？洗埋香港班新移民腦就最好。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上只係自己突然諗到，未細諗，求討論！純粹見未有人做，覺得可行，希望大家幫手推po !!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace6cab069dafa9216bc431ccb2e3e8e89d81db8","tid":1636537,"uid":154040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:27:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">蒙面冇罪<br />\n立法無理<br />\n全民口罩<br />\n以抗暴政</span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jqqtpR7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjqqtpR7.png&h=c55a1693&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wwTrbw7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwwTrbw7.jpg&h=4a707df5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uXCzkqs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuXCzkqs.jpg&h=df8b5cf9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/URsb65t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FURsb65t.jpg&h=edfd0767&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VOFQDb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVOFQDb8.jpg&h=c50826a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S5Z2uiO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS5Z2uiO.jpg&h=a2d5ed70&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yNGz4R9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyNGz4R9.jpg&h=a9a4322a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f8f525eec6cd20b802543bb7076b5ac30cee015","tid":1636537,"uid":177088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:28:43.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"202d70d4d7ff6d3e551d4960bdc1f95d0bcfb86e","tid":1636537,"uid":177088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"